{
  "stem": "6719.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went up to him and I said to him, my parents were killed today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's that date in the Jewish calendar?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I did not know this was the 22nd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't have a calendar with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, today is the 30th of Pesach-- Passover.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how I found that it was the 22nd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when I had the information that the transport left on the 20th from Belgium, later on, then I knew that this was the right date.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where I have my yahrzeit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know what that is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That I don't have to translate, I don't think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then things became very tricky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tricky in such a way that I got scared that this guy is going to get me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This guy, Hans Kuehneman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I tried to get out of that place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you can't just walk away from it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have to go through the, uh, the office of the people that put the work kommandos together and all that, just like an office.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't an office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The office was outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to my friend-- another-- you know, funny enough, this is the third Seppl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Seppl.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Means Joseph.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like Dolphy to Adolf.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The real name is Joseph, and the abbreviation in Bavaria and in Austria is Seppl, S-E-P-P-L, Or Sepp, S-E-P-P.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this guy was a-- a murderer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a-- a-- a [GERMAN], in other words, a green triangle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He came from jail somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how they brought these kapos in there in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And because again, of his dialect-- he came from Bavaria-- this is how I discovered him, and he discovered me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I brought him something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I brought him a ring.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
